                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Box                                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "BX"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      12                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      04                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      14                   to   v-lto                  .
           move      77                   to   v-pto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Messaggio nel box                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      65                   to   v-car                  .
           move      13                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      06                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-err-box-err-msg    to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Parentesi quadre di delimitazione               *
